        "description": "Women's Health Wednesdays: Birth Control and Reproductive Health\t\n\nHave questions about birth control options? Concerned about your menstrual cycle? Women's Health Wednesdays are a great time to talk through your reproductive health in a comfortable, private setting.\n \nEvery Wednesday from 1:00 to 4:30 PM with Dr. Hernandez and Pamela Cameau. Book through ZocDoc.\n \nWe are here to offer judgment-free, expert guidance tailored to you.",
