        "description": "Chronic Disease Management at Midtown\t\n\nManaging a chronic condition like diabetes, high blood pressure, or high cholesterol? Our Midtown primary care team provides ongoing, personalized management to keep you healthy and out of the hospital.\n \nWe handle regular monitoring, medication management, and lifestyle guidance. Think of us as your long-term health partner.",
