        "description": "Annual Wellness Exams - Covered by Most Insurance\t\n\nYour yearly physical is one of the most important things you can do for your health. At MR Primary Care in Midtown, we make it easy and stress-free.\n \nWe review your health history, run necessary labs, update vaccines, and create a personalized care plan, all in one visit.\n\n Book your annual exam today.",
