        "description": "Women's Health Wednesdays: What to Expect\t\n\nCurious about Women's Health Wednesdays? Here is how it works:\n \nEvery Wednesday from 1:00 PM to 4:30 PM\n\nIn person at MR Primary Care, 10022\n\nSeen by Dr. Hernandez and Pamela Cameau\n \nInitial visits and procedures run about 45 minutes. Follow-up visits are shorter, around 15 minutes, so you always have the right amount of time for your care.\n \nOur goal is to keep things simple by handling your evaluation, testing, and follow-up all in one place. Book through ZocDoc.",
