        "description": "Introducing Women's Health Wednesdays\n\nWe are excited to offer Women's Health Wednesdays at MR Primary Care in Midtown!\n \n Every Wednesday from 1:00 PM to 4:30 PM, Dr. Hernandez and Pamela Cameau see patients for a range of women's health visits including:\n - Annual exams and Pap smears\n - Birth control counseling\n - Menstrual health concerns\n - Menopause and perimenopause\n - Hormone-related issues\n - Mental health conditions\n - UTI and STD testing and treatment\n \n Book through ZocDoc. In-person visits at our 10022 location.",
