          "description": "Dr. Liakeas has been my primarily care physician for going on 15 years now, and his exceptional care runs laps around other doctors I\u2019ve seen over the years. Healthcare can be a tough subject for most due to inadequate care from providers, but Dr. Liakeas always takes the time and effort to make sure you feel your needs are met and your questions are answered. The best doctor in NYC, in my opinion.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGeGNGaDBkR0V3ZG5wVFQzazBRbFpXTUdGb2QwRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xff1c9baadef1fe2e!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjFxcFh0dGEwdnpTT3k0QlZWMGFod0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
