          "description": "I would have loved to give 5 starts because Dr. Shavalian is great!\nCaring and professional!\nUnfortunately however it is absolutely impossible to talk to a person when calling and they NEVER call back. The girls at the front desk are instructed NOT to answer the phone which is extremely unsettling. Being a doctor's office when patients call they expect to be connected to a DOCTOR or have their questioned answered. Patient will call a doctor's office because they need a doctor not to press button and have a recording telling them to leave a message and that they will TEXT back after 24 hours. A patients needs a reply when they call not after 24 hours! This is not acceptable and needs to improve. It sure has changed from when Dr. Liakeas was in charge.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pRemFVbEZlbXRzUVdKSVEybE1RMHhsV0VOa1UyYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xff1c9baadef1fe2e!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjQzaUlFemtsQWJIQ2lMQ0xlWENkU2c%7C%7C?hl=en",
